NEXT_PUBLIC_APP_URL=http://127.0.0.1:3000

# Social sign-in (LinkedIn OIDC, Google): enable providers in Supabase Dashboard → Authentication → Providers.
# LinkedIn app → Auth → Authorized redirect URL must include your Supabase callback, e.g.
#   https://<project-ref>.supabase.co/auth/v1/callback
# Supabase → Authentication → URL Configuration → Redirect URLs must include every app origin you use, e.g.
#   http://127.0.0.1:3000/auth/callback  http://localhost:3000/auth/callback  https://your-domain/auth/callback
# The app shows Google/LinkedIn only when NODE_ENV=production (hosted). Local next dev is email/password only.

